{"tid":1617341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"薑同綠茶其實對身體有好多好處","createTime":"2019-10-03T17:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T17:49:44.000Z","uid":135554,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ce6068ed1a2026be29ca3f368ab3f0908709feb8","tid":1617341,"uid":135554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:49:10.000Z","msg":"薑對人既好處有好多，從中醫既角度，薑能夠解表散寒，溫中止嘔，化痰止咳。用於風寒感冒，胃寒嘔吐，寒痰咳嗽，腹痛腹瀉、中魚蟹毒等。<br />\n<br />\n而綠茶對人體既好處更大，綠茶所含的兒茶素具抗氧化、消毒殺菌及消炎功能，可減低患腸胃疾病的風險，所以它一直被說成具有強身健體之功效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110403940298217/posts/134912891180655/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110403940298217%2Fposts%2F134912891180655%2F&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=12ad6866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110403940298217/posts/134912891180655/</a>"},{"pid":"026d5558f945943f220ef7ad7a930c248339e62a","tid":1617341,"uid":135554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:49:29.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔知原來咁有益"},{"pid":"60791eaf7471e3cea47bcfa9693bf61d40b28f8a","tid":1617341,"uid":135554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:49:44.000Z","msg":"咁就要食多啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}